UID:pTB-w78AhJU0Qm3r8gHII
SUMMARY:America: The Happy Trails Tour 2026
DTSTAMP:20260411T040850Z
DTSTART:20260612T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Paramount Theatre is located at 911 Pine Street in Downtown
	 Seattle. There is a ticket limit of 8 tickets per person and per credit c
	ard on this event. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have their orde
	rs canceled at the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No refunds or 
	exchanges. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue rese
	rves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each p
	erson must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no
	 elevator. Stairs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search
	 at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When 
	purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by emai
	l if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you m
	ay reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses 
	an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and th
	eir companions. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to t
	he balcony levels.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/america-the-happy-trail
	s-tour-2026-seattle-washington-06-11-2026/event/0F006435B12ABE0F
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/america-the-happy-trails-tour-2026-seattle
